import { Box, Typography } from "@mui/material";

const ReviewCard = ({ review }) => {
    return(
        <Box
            display="flex"
            flexDirection="column"
            alignItems="center"
            justifyContent="center"
            width="100%"
            backgroundColor="lightgreen"
            padding="1rem"
        >
            <Box
                width="90%"
                height="60%"
            >
                <Typography>
                    {review["review"]}
                </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box
                width="90%"
                height="30%"
                display="flex"
                justifyContent="space-between"
            >
                <Box
                    width="60%"
                    display="flex"
                    justifyContent="flex-start"
                    alignItems='flex-start'
                    flexDirection="column"
                >
                    <Typography>
                        {review["name"]}
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        {review["rating"]}
                    </Typography>
                </Box>
                <Box
                    width="40%"
                    display="flex"
                    justifyContent="flex-end"
                    alignItems='flex-end'
                >

                </Box>

            </Box>

        </Box>
    )
}

export default ReviewCard;
